textAfterTable: Justin is a 2011 graduate of Saint Mary's High School, where his team won the State Championship and he was named All-Long Island and the team MVP his senior season. Junior year...Played in every game, while starting 26...Averaged 8.7 points and 3.4 rebounds a game...Ranked fourth on the team with 27 steals. Sophomore year...Appeared in 27 games, starting in 11 with 18.5 minutes per game. Averaged 4.9 points and 1.9 boards per game.
